### Example Heuristic Functions:

1. Larger bins are better: priority is bin capacity.
2. Bins with more space left are better: priority is (max_bin_capacity - bin_size).
3. Bins with similar size to item are better: priority is 1 / |item - bin_size|.
4. Bins with less space are better: priority is bin_size.
5. Bins with higher density (space filled) are better: priority is bin_size / max_bin_capacity.
