Heuristic 1: Bins with more space have higher priority. Priority = (bin_size - current_usage) 

Heuristic 2: Bins with less space have higher priority. Priority = current_usage

Heuristic 3: Bins with similar size to the item have higher priority. Priority = |item - bin_size|

Heuristic 4: Bins with both similar size and more space have higher priority. Priority = (bin_size - current_usage) * |item - bin_size|

Heuristic 5: Bins with more space and smaller size have higher priority. Priority = (bin_size - current_usage) / bin_size

