Heuristic 8: Bins with similar size and less space have higher priority. Priority = (current_usage) * |item - bin_size|

Heuristic 9: Bins with more space and lower variability have higher priority. Priority = (bin_size - current_usage) / np.std(bins)

Heuristic 10: Bins with more space and higher variability have higher priority. Priority = (bin_size - current_usage) * np.std(bins)

